event-rpc: Event::RPC (Event based Client/Server RPC framework)
event-rpc:
event-rpc: Event::RPC supports you in developing Event based
event-rpc: networking client/server applications with transparent
event-rpc: object/method access from the client to the server. Network
event-rpc: communication is optionally encrypted using
event-rpc: IO::Socket::SSL. Several event loop managers are supported
event-rpc: due to an extensible API. Currently Event and Glib are
event-rpc: implemented.
